      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "If the core of your purpose feels gone, that heavy weight you're carrying is immense, and it's okay to feel overwhelmed by it. When everything feels like a burden, sometimes the simplest act of existing—just breathing through the next hour—is the bravest thing you can do. Please consider reaching out to a professional who can help you navigate these feelings of emptiness and hopelessness.",
      "source": "target",
